Text:
{d}nanna dumu-saŋ {d}en-lil₂-la₂ lugal-a-ni\dat ur-{d}namma nita kalag-ga lugal urim₅{ki}-ma lugal ki-en-gi ki-uri-ke₄ lu₂ e₂ {d}nanna\gen\abs in-du₃-a\erg niŋ₂ ul-li₂-a-ke₄
5el3 pa\abs mu-na-e₃ gaba a-ab-ka-ka
5al2 ki-saₓ(SAR)-a
5al2 nam-ga-eš₈\abs bi₂-sa₂ ma₂ ma₂-gan\abs šu-na
5al2 mu-ni-gi₄
